Want an easy tool to get images out of your videos? Use SnapMotion — a simple tool to help you get just the visuals you need from your video files. Rotate or flip your videos before capture, open quickly from Finder or Photos, and get as many stills as you like with no delay with SnapMotion.
Capture in top quality
Open 4K and 8K videos with no lag and get high quality captures with SnapMotion. Forget about haphazard screenshots that take too much time to capture just right and are blurry more often than not. Get frames from your videos in the highest quality possible with handy SnapMotion tools.
Open videos easily
Waste no time when opening your videos. Open the files in Finder, Photos, Files directly to SnapMotion. More good news? You can also open your videos to SnapMotion via links, making your snapping easy and fast — no need to move your files or download in advance.
